flowchart TD
    client([Web client])

    subgraph backend [Backend]
        auth[User authentication]
        api[Key directory API]
        ethclient[Ethereum API client]
    end

    subgraph eth [Ethereum]
        rpc[JSON-RPC endpoint]
        node[Ethereum network]
        contract[Smart contract]
        chain[(Replicated state<br/>key directory)]
    end

    client -->|HTTPS| auth
    auth --> api
    api --> ethclient
    ethclient -->|eth_sendRawTransaction| rpc
    rpc --> node
    node --> contract
    contract --> chain
    client -.eth_call, eth_getLogs.-> rpc